blogs.title: Sinus
blogs.description: Sinus problems are a common reason people visit their doctor, particularly during cold and allergy seasons. The sinuses are not just empty spaces in the skull â€” they are an integral part of the respiratory system, playing roles in air filtration, voice resonance, and overall nasal health.
